{"name":"Silvoy's Company","size":"large","type":"Humanoid Group","tag":"","alignment":"neutral good","hitDice":"8","armorName":"chain mail","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"60 (8d10 + 16)","speedDesc":"80 ft. mounted, 30 ft standing.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"9","wisPoints":"13","chaPoints":"11","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"2","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The centaur can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The centaur regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the centaur can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the centaur can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The centaur can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the centaur's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the centaur's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the centaur dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Pike","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1d10 + 2] piercing damage."},{"name":"Javelin","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, range 30/120ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1d6 + 2] piercing damage."},{"name":"Form Up!","desc":"Up to 10 allied soldiers can move their speed towards [MON]. Each member of the defensive formation gets a +5 to their AC."},{"name":"Strike Together!","desc":"[2d4]+1 soldiers may attack with their spear. Soldiers attacking the same target have advantage."},{"name":"Volley (1/day)","desc":"The soldiers throw their spears. Choose a point within 30ft, each creature within a 10ft sphere of the point must make a DC [DEX SAVE] dexterity save, or take [4d6+4] damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Advance!","desc":"[MON] and his defensive formation may move up to 15ft."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Protect Civilans (2/round)","desc":"If a civilian is targeted by an attack, a soldier may move his speed to leave the defensive formation and interpose themselves to change the target of the attack to themselves."},{"name":"Brace (1/round)","desc":"If a member of the defensive formation is struck by an attack, they gain resistance to the damage."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Silvoy","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}